statement:
WITH
    CAT2CAT AS (
    SELECT
        h.cat1 category_level_1,
        h.cat2 AS category_level_2,
        v.sku child_sku
    FROM BI.`s43$prod_master_v` v
    LEFT JOIN BI.`s43$cat_hier` h on h.cat_id = v.cat_id
    LEFT JOIN BI.`s43$cat` c on c.id = v.cat_id
    LEFT JOIN S0043.BRAND b on b.id = v.brand_id
    LEFT JOIN BI.`s43$prod_bucket` d ON v.bucket_id = d.id
    LEFT JOIN BI.`STOCK_MASTER_V` s on s.sku = v.sku
    WHERE PARENT_CATEGORY = 'Аптека'
    ),
    SUBORDERSENTRIES AS (
        SELECT DISTINCT
            CAST(ordercode AS VARCHAR(100)) AS suborder_id,
            sku AS child_sku
        FROM BI.s43$orderentries
        WHERE
            sku IN (SELECT DISTINCT child_sku FROM CAT2CAT )
    ),
    SUBORDERS AS (
        SELECT
            cart_id AS order_id,
            ordercode AS suborder_id,
            DATE(orderdate) AS dd_order,
            cityfr AS city_ordered_from,
            totalprice AS amt_suborder
        FROM BI.s43$ord_v SO
        WHERE
            DATE(SO.orderdate) BETWEEN DATE('2025-10-01') AND DATE(NOW())
            AND
            orderstatus = 'Выдан'
            AND
            bad != 1
            AND
            approve = 1
            AND
            cityfr IN ('Нур-Султан', 'Алматы')
            AND
            CAST(ordercode AS VARCHAR(100)) IN (SELECT DISTINCT suborder_id FROM SUBORDERSENTRIES)
    ),
    COMPLETE_SUBORDERS AS (
        SELECT
            SO.order_id,
            SO.suborder_id,
            SO.dd_order,
            SO.amt_suborder,
            SO.city_ordered_from,
            SOE.child_sku,
            C2C.category_level_1,
            C2C.category_level_2
        FROM SUBORDERS AS SO
        LEFT JOIN SUBORDERSENTRIES AS SOE ON SOE.suborder_id = SO.suborder_id
        LEFT JOIN CAT2CAT AS C2C
        ON SOE.child_sku = C2C.child_sku
    ),
    DATA AS (
        SELECT
            CS1.*,
            FLAG. is_suborder_drug,
            IF(cntSO_total >= 2, 1, 0) AS is_cart_split,
            IF(cntSO_drugs >= 2, 1, 0) AS is_cart_drugs_split
        FROM COMPLETE_SUBORDERS  AS CS1
        LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT
                order_id,
                COUNT(DISTINCT  suborder_id) AS cntSO_total,
                COUNT(DISTINCT IF(category_level_2 = 'Лекарства', suborder_id, NULL)) AS cntSO_drugs
            FROM COMPLETE_SUBORDERS
            GROUP BY
                1
        ) AS SS ON SS.order_id = CS1.order_id
        LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT
                suborder_id, MAX(category_level_2 = 'Лекарства') AS is_suborder_drug
            FROM COMPLETE_SUBORDERS
            GROUP BY
                1
        ) AS FLAG
        ON FLAG.suborder_id = CS1.suborder_id
    )
SELECT *
FROM DATA;
